1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:01:00,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

2
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:01,160
Kill everyone but the children.

3
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,640
Don't go there!

4
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,560
Don't go there.

5
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,040
Mother!

6
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,000
Mother!

7
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,640
Mother!

8
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,920
Stop!

9
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,320
You wear painted skins?

10
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:45,000
You're not from the Shilin Sect.

11
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,560
Who are you exactly?

12
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,720
What are you after?

13
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:44,280
The Frost Spell. The Formless Moon Sect.

14
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,440
Wu Wangyan?

15
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:10,240
You always wanted to know
what secret I was hiding.

16
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,520
Now you have your answer.

17
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:27,720
The Star Stone…

18
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,000
Give it back!

19
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,040
Dream on.

20
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,280
The sachet…

21
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,320
Oh no!

22
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:52,080
Threatening me with him won't work.
I can't undo the petrification.

23
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,720
I can't do it.

24
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,400
Then I'll kill him!

25
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:07,280
The stone thorn has my runes on it.

26
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,560
If I cast the spell…

27
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,280
you'll die instantly.

28
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:18,160
Do you choose death,
or do you help me free my people?

29
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,280
Qing Yi!

30
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,040
The Dragon Deity's Power.

31
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,280
You have it,

32
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,400
so why no dragon birthmark?

33
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,000
The Dragon clan…

34
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,159
Birthmark…

35
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,760
Your birthmark is so interesting.

36
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,040
It looks like a heart
made of flowing water.

37
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,040
How did I never see it?

38
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,720
You're not Wu Wangyan.

39
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:57,000
You're not her!

40
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:01,240
You're looking for a child
with a dragon birthmark.

41
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,920
Then I know who you are.

42
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,600
That's right.

43
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,880
She's Jiu Ying.

44
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,960
Little Nine.

45
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:35,760
Or maybe…

46
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,600
I should call you by your true name…

47
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:44,480
Jiu Ying.

48
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,880
Who sent you here?

49
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,520
Why pretend to be a Shilin Sect member?

50
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,880
It… It's Jiu Ying.

51
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,400
You know of me?

52
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:06,320
The first time I saw
those nine spots on you,

53
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:09,080
I suspected it was you.

54
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:13,080
Those nine markings on your head
are quite pretty.

55
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:15,960
So I'll call you Little Nine.

56
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:21,680
Later, you found out
we weren't the real Man Man and Di Zhu.

57
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,840
If you were dead,

58
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:30,680
those two demons
who possess Man Man and Di Zhu

59
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,240
would never get the Star Stone.

60
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,680
The only one who could stay by us
and eavesdrop on our every word

61
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,840
was Little Nine.

62
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:43,640
But Little Nine
was just an ordinary, harmless snake.

63
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:47,040
Relax. The blood didn't turn dark.

64
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:51,680
So, I had to wait for you to slip up,
to reveal your true form.

65
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,960
I failed twice…

66
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:11,720
but in the end, I caught you.

67
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:16,400
Just a bit too late,
since you've grown your third head.

68
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:21,000
I don't quite understand
what you're saying.

69
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:25,880
But it sounds like you know me well,

70
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,920
like an old friend.

71
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,720
Indeed.

72
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,200
Very well.

73
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,440
All your scheming,

74
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,920
just to get a look at my true form?

75
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:45,920
Because in the end,
you'll become the Demon King,

76
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:50,240
destroying the whole world,
yet no one knows your origin.

77
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:56,800
So, I wanted to find out
what exactly you are.

78
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,800
In the beginning,

79
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,240
I was just a snake egg

80
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:08,560
buried in this earth
for millions of years, unable to hatch.

81
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:10,720
The egg was filled with deadly venom.

82
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:15,240
The Aodeng people migrated here
and were poisoned one after another.

83
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,760
They thought it was a plague.

84
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:22,040
Then the Star Stone fell from the sky,

85
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,800
bringing heavenly fire.

86
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:31,800
The heat of the flames hatched you.

87
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:36,560
I broke out of my shell,
absorbed the Star Stone's power,

88
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:37,840
and became a demon.

89
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,120
The egg disappeared.

90
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,920
The Aodeng people
stopped getting poisoned.

91
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:46,680
They thought it was a blessing
from the Star Stone.

92
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:49,360
After I hatched,

93
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:54,600
the first person I saw was Di Zhu.

94
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:08,640
But I was newly born, my power weak.

95
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:12,400
I could only take Di Zhu's blood
and briefly possess her.

96
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:17,840
That way, I could go
into the cave every night

97
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:21,280
to absorb the Star Stone's power
and grow stronger.

98
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:25,160
To keep others from getting the Stone,

99
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,760
you started killing.

100
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:33,680
The Star Stone's power
gave me a second venomous head.

101
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:39,120
I smeared venom on a hairpin
to kill those who coveted the Stone.

102
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,360
But the venom couldn't kill demons.

103
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,480
So…

104
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,760
I could only frame you.

105
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:51,040
Too bad you didn't succeed.

106
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,480
True.

107
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,720
But I got something unexpected.

108
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:04,840
I found a power source
even stronger than the Star Stone.

109
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,600
Killing.

110
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:10,080
No, not killing. It's fear.

111
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:14,760
I realized, the more people died,

112
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,800
the more the Aodeng people feared,

113
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,520
the stronger I became.

114
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:24,000
In just a few days,

115
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:28,760
I've already grown my third head.

116
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:33,400
Even without the Star Stone,

117
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:36,760
as long as the world
is filled with despair,

118
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:40,840
fear, and hatred,

119
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,760
I'll have an endless supply of power.

120
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,920
Soon enough,

121
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:51,080
all nine of my heads will be fully grown.

122
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:58,600
With all nine heads,

123
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:02,120
Jiu Ying can break each head
into nine spirit fragments.

124
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:05,200
Eighty-one pieces
scattered across the world.

125
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:08,480
That's why this land
is overrun with people

126
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,760
controlled by Jiu Ying.

127
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:14,840
The Six-Eyed Butterflies under Jiu Ying
planted pupae inside us.

128
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:16,520
We have no choice but to obey.

129
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:19,280
Wu Zhiqi was already going
to give the Star Stone to Jiu Ying,

130
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:21,560
to bring it to the battlefield
and destroy humanity.

131
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:26,400
Why control you
and arrange for us to steal it?

132
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:31,800
Because… the Star Stone
wasn't meant to destroy humanity.

133
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:35,640
It was to make humans
and demons destroy each other.

134
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,800
What?

135
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,960
The Yuan Clay Incident,
which sparked the war,

136
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:42,120
seemed like an accident,

137
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,880
but it was also schemed by Jiu Ying.

138
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,520
You mean Yuan's death

139
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:52,640
wasn't an accident?

140
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:54,480
It wasn't just him.

141
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,960
There are countless others

142
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:59,080
you'd never suspect
possessed by Jiu Ying's spirit.

143
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:00,800
They walk among us,

144
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:05,560
constantly stirring conflict
between our races, igniting battles.

145
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:11,360
And all this strife and hatred
makes Jiu Ying stronger.

146
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,280
She even slaughtered the nine Dragons.

147
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:18,520
No wonder they say
Jiu Ying can't be killed.

148
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:21,880
Turns out, even sealed
by the nine dragon sons,

149
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,960
you're still causing chaos.

150
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:30,760
They thought sealing my nine heads
would destroy me for good.

151
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,720
Too bad

152
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:36,240
I'd already scattered countless
spirit fragments across the world.

153
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:41,840
Each piece can attach to a living being.

154
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:52,080
Once it attaches,

155
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:54,200
it waits for a moment
when the host's mind wavers,

156
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:55,480
then takes control.

157
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:59,880
As long as one piece remains,
Jiu Ying cannot die.

158
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,680
You might as well give up.

159
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,720
No. You're wrong.

160
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:08,280
The Dragon Deity
will defeat Jiu Ying in the end.

161
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:12,920
All 81 spirit fragments
will be destroyed one by one.

162
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:15,240
That annoying Shilin Sect

163
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:19,640
has been hunting for my spirit fragments.

164
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:21,680
I have to kill Chi Wen,

165
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:23,800
break the seal,

166
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:26,920
and get my heads back.

167
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:31,120
So you've been searching
for the dragon's descendants.

168
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,640
Because only a dragon…

169
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,040
Can kill a dragon.

170
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,960
The Six-Eyed Butterflies
gave us the glowing worm.

171
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,840
Once it's inside the Star Stone,

172
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:51,920
it will devour his insides,
make him lose control,

173
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:54,160
and cause an explosion.

174
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,320
Where's the Star Stone?

175
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:38,960
What do we do now?
Where are we taking him?

176
00:18:39,040 --> 00:18:40,080
We can't go anywhere.

177
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:58,120
The Six-Eyed Butterfly…

178
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,920
is actually two people.

179
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,080
That's right.

180
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:08,000
Unlike you, we're inseparable,
loving brothers.

181
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,080
Watch out!

182
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,640
You've got it wrong. We're not with him.

183
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:34,920
Threatening us with him won't work.
You should just kill him.

184
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:37,880
Are you sure?

185
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:42,240
The look on the person
behind you says otherwise.

186
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:46,080
If you don't want him dead, come with us.

187
00:19:57,200 --> 00:20:00,680
Don't forget he imprisoned you
for all those years.

188
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:06,960
You said earlier he secretly helped us

189
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:09,880
by letting me go.

190
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,480
All these years,

191
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:20,440
in that tiny space, he was my only friend.

192
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,120
If you no longer care
about the Star Stone,

193
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:35,480
then why did you attack me at the wedding?

194
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:47,920
- Kiss!
- Kiss!

195
00:20:55,120 --> 00:20:56,400
Come out, Little Nine!

196
00:20:57,040 --> 00:20:58,600
I simply wanted you dead.

197
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:15,800
Tian Di!

198
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:32,760
Let Wu Zhiqi go! Stop!

199
00:21:58,480 --> 00:22:02,840
You're covered in wounds,
yet you can't bear to hurt her.

200
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:05,200
How devoted.

201
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:09,440
Let's see how long you can last.

202
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,560
Don't be rash!

203
00:23:22,520 --> 00:23:24,840
Oh no. He's losing control of his power!

204
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:37,720
Tian Di… No!

205
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,640
Yuan Xizai!

206
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:16,160
So this is the Star Stone
exit Master Bai Ze mentioned?

207
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:17,680
This stone tablet?

208
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:19,840
It's Wu Shiguang's master's grave.

209
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:22,320
Stop bickering. Quick, smear the blood.

210
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,240
Okay. Got it.

211
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,440
Wu Shiguang would be surprised

212
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:28,120
that the keepsake of our friendship I kept
would save his life years later.

213
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,800
Why isn't it working?

214
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,720
That liar Bai Ze!

215
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:06,280
Are they really going to die
in the disasters?

216
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:39,520
Master… What's happening?

217
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:41,600
Father!

218
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:43,760
Mother!

219
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:44,920
Shiguang!

220
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:04,760
Quick, take him and go!

221
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:07,520
I won't! I have to save my parents!

222
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:08,600
Father!

223
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:27,440
What are you waiting for? Go after them!

224
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:18,280
Lu Wuyi!

225
00:28:24,560 --> 00:28:25,560
Lu Wuyi!

226
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:43,080
- Oh no.
- What's happening to Wu Zhiqi?

227
00:28:43,760 --> 00:28:45,960
The third head, the head of frenzy.

228
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:50,160
It drives a person mad,
making their demon power run wild.

229
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:57,520
If Wu Zhiqi loses control,
it'll cause the Hurricane Catastrophe.

230
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:01,080
I've figured out Jiu Ying's origin.

231
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:03,520
Let's go. We'll use
the Star Stone to leave.

232
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,320
- Okay.
- Let's go.

233
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,120
Where's the Star Stone?

234
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:27,480
You go first.
You can turn into sand and leave.

235
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:30,520
Let's go together!

236
00:30:17,760 --> 00:30:19,680
Once we get the Star Stone,

237
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:22,960
we can use our power
to leave the illusion.

238
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,800
You…

239
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:58,240
He…

240
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:03,440
He's Yuan Wuhuo, the butterfly demon.

241
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,120
He went in too?

242
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:09,600
When the Star Stone's pull
was strongest earlier,

243
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:12,040
I almost got sucked in.

244
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:23,240
The butterfly demon hiding
in the shadows pushed me away.

245
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:26,080
But he got pulled in himself.

246
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:30,920
So, in the past they're living in,

247
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:35,240
who is the true owner of that time?

248
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:39,800
That past was shared by the two brothers.

249
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:43,680
They are both the owners
and witnesses to each other.

250
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:47,600
You're not that Yuan Wuhuo.

251
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:50,640
You're the butterfly demon, Yuan Wuhuo.

252
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,200
That's right.

253
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:57,000
So you've been acting this whole time.

254
00:31:58,760 --> 00:31:59,600
That's right.

255
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:02,720
How else could I make you
lower your guard,

256
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:04,400
help me get the Star Stone,

257
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:06,880
and leave this place?

258
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:10,600
So you were behind it before too.

259
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,080
Exactly.

260
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:16,520
I tried to kill Tian Di

261
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:19,720
to turn him back into the Star Stone.

262
00:32:20,520 --> 00:32:22,040
But it didn't work.

263
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:26,840
All that struggling was pointless.

264
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:50,520
Did you really think

265
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,640
I was your brother?

266
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,600
Aren't you?

267
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,560
No.

268
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:03,400
Then why do you look exactly like me?

269
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:05,840
You're wrong.

270
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:10,480
Know your place.

271
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:13,440
You look like me.

272
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:16,560
I…

273
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:26,560
Who am I?

274
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:31,120
You'll never know.

275
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:36,920
Stay here forever.

276
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,679
Yuan Xizai!

277
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,800
Why did I lose my power?

278
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:36,360
Quick, heal him!

279
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,679
Hurry!

280
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:39,679
Xizai! Xizai!

281
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:42,719
Save him! Save him!

282
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:59,040
I can't hold it together much longer.

283
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:03,440
The Star Stone must not shatter.
I still need it to save my people.

284
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:05,320
Is there any way?

285
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:06,920
Yes.

286
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:08,480
What is it?

287
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,280
What is it?

288
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:13,360
The Dragon Deity's Power.

289
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:17,400
It can restore anything
and bring the dead back to life.

290
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:28,920
Dragon hearts as one,

291
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:31,360
all to source return,

292
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:34,280
all barriers break!

293
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,320
Dragon hearts as one,

294
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:11,600
all to source return,

295
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,800
all barriers break!

296
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:48,960
Master Jiu Ying truly has
flawless foresight.

297
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:57,240
I infused my demonic energy
into a fragment of the Star Stone.

298
00:36:57,840 --> 00:37:01,080
Once it joins with the piece Wu Zhiqi has,

299
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:04,840
the entire Star Stone
will shatter completely.

300
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:09,200
Wu Zhiqi will surely sacrifice himself,

301
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:12,280
releasing
the Dragon Deity's Power to fix it.

302
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:15,320
Then you'll have your chance
to seize his power.

303
00:37:54,600 --> 00:37:55,920
Give up.

304
00:37:56,640 --> 00:38:01,200
Take after Xiaowei,
and you'll share her fate.

305
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:22,680
Bai Ze, you already gave 70% of your power
to that false Dragon Deity.

306
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:27,160
And you used another 20%
to fix the Star Stone.

307
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:32,040
With the 10% left,
you want to break my barrier?

308
00:38:32,640 --> 00:38:34,400
What a joke.

309
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:39,480
Or maybe…

310
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:44,600
you could try using
the Dragon Deity's Power.

311
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:05,920
Now we're really trapped here.

312
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:07,800
It's all my fault.

313
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:11,400
It's all my fault. I'm sorry.

314
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:17,880
At least we know Jiu Ying's origin,
that's something.

315
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:22,120
And we found out something else,
even better.

316
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,840
What's it?

317
00:39:24,640 --> 00:39:26,040
Jiu Ying's weakness.

318
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,320
What's his weakness?

319
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:32,120
The same weakness as mine.

320
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:36,600
Look out!

321
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:41,640
Ji Ling! Ji Ling!

322
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:47,360
Ji Ling! Hold on to me! Don't let go!

323
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:52,480
Lu Wuyi!

324
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:58,720
What are you doing?

325
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:04,000
A spike will help…

326
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:20,880
When disaster strikes,
lovers stay together.

327
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:27,400
"Live together, die together"?
That's just a story to fool girls.

328
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:32,160
I don't like him enough to die for him.

329
00:40:43,600 --> 00:40:44,480
The Star Stone!

330
00:40:49,520 --> 00:40:50,400
Let go!

331
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,240
No!

332
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:54,240
Let go of the other hand!

333
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:57,400
Take out the spike! Trust me!

334
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:05,440
Let's take a gamble.

335
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:08,360
If we lose, we just stay here.

336
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,640
And I'll marry you!

337
00:42:46,720 --> 00:42:47,800
You're here.
